realize

public SimpleApplication realize(SimpleApplicationSchema schema,
                                 String name,
                                 ApplicationConsole console)
                          throws IOException
Realizes an instance of an Application.

Parameters:
schema - the ApplicationSchema to use for realizing the Application
name - the name of the application
console - the ApplicationConsole that will be used for I/O by the realized Application. This may be null if not required
Returns:
an Application representing the application realized by the ApplicationBuilder
Throws:
IOException - when a problem occurs while starting the application
